flowchart LR
  Register[registerUser] --> CreateUser[CreateUserFacade]
  CreateUser --> KC[Keycloak user + role + password]
  CreateUser --> DBUser[UserService saves User]
  CreateUser --> Matrix[Matrix user provisioning]
  CreateUser --> CreateSession[CreateNewSessionFacade / CreateSessionFacade]
  CreateSession --> SessionDB[Session + SessionData]
  CreateSession --> Room[Matrix holding/direct room]
  Assign[assignSession] --> AssignFacade[AssignSessionFacade]
  AssignFacade --> SessionUpdate[Session status + consultant]
  AssignFacade --> Rocket[Update Rocket.Chat group members]
  AssignFacade --> Mail[Email notification]
  AssignFacade --> Stats[Statistics event]
